code: @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     }     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) {         return false.     }     TaskManagerInfo that = (TaskManagerInfo) o.     return dataPort == that.dataPort && lastHeartbeat == that.lastHeartbeat && numberSlots == that.numberSlots && numberAvailableSlots == that.numberAvailableSlots && Objects.equals(resourceId, that.resourceId) && Objects.equals(address, that.address) && Objects.equals(hardwareDescription, that.hardwareDescription). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(resourceId, address, dataPort, lastHeartbeat, numberSlots, numberAvailableSlots, hardwareDescription). }
